## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of data and perspectives primarily from U.S.-based sources. The focus on systemic and logistical barriers may overlook cultural or psychological factors influencing youth voter turnout. Additionally, the data is drawn from articles and studies up to 2023, which may not fully capture recent changes in youth engagement or voting reforms.